            code: unique identifier. Has to match the code of its texture
            construction_cost: construction cost in resources
            culture_per_turn: the player will gain x culture per turn for this building
            resource_per_field: for each adjacent field of resources, a maximum amount of x can be obtained
            resource_per_turn: similar to culture_per_turn.
                                The player will gain this without the need of adjacent resource fields
            sight_range: Upon construction, every hexagon with this distance or less gets revealed
            food_consumption: building consumes x food per turn
            construction_time: it will take x turns to build this building, before its state is active
            defensive_value: if attacked, the defencive strength is this value
            flag_x, flag_y: offset in pixels to the center of the building where to place the flag
            grant_pop: the building gives x amount of free population (this value can be negative)
